Addons (modifiers) for OpenCart.  Tested on OC v.2.3.0
1. DisableEmptyorder - prohibits the formation of an empty order.

2. Instok - adds a display of the availability of goods ("In stock", "pre-ordered" ETC) in the product cards in the catalog.

3. LinksinMenu - adds to the top menu (directory menu) section for the pages for which the "Do not display in Footer" parameter is set.  Used to add the partition of the articles to the directory menu.

4. PriceByRequest - for goods with the wrong price (price = 0) installs instead of zero price value "Price on request".

5. Watermark - adds to all images (with the exception of banners) Watermark.  File watermark.png worth it to be in / Images /
